  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Survival Escape Room,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou've been kidnapped and you only have so much time to escape. Keep in mind there is only one exit. Use your light up headband to see more clearly in the dark. Watch out, there's monsters lurking nearby.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControls: <br />\r\n<br />\r\nW,A,S,D to move<br />\r\nSpace Bar to jump<br />\r\nF to use light up headband<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNew escape rooms will be released in every update.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck!",
